<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_33d096cd3773.aspx"><b>二子乘舟</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson33d096cd3773">
二子乘舟，泛泛其景。愿言思子，中心养养！<br />二子乘舟，泛泛其逝。愿言思子，不瑕有害！
</div>
